description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'August Race: Week 3 of 5' from the channel Mac Evans.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Competitor and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: Explode with power and speed during 5-minute pieces with Mac before going all out for a final 1-minute effort.

Max rhythm: 30, Format: Power...
